videos.description: Joel Embiid is introduced to a mixture of cheers and boos following his shushing of the 76ers' home crowd Sunday against the Bulls.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid introduced to mixed reaction from home crowd) 2020/02/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid introduced to mixed reaction from home crowd

videos.description: Joel Embiid grabs an offensive rebound and scores an and-1 for his first bucket of the night, then smiles and raises his arms to an ovation from the 76ers' crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid scores and-1, smiles for 76ers’ crowd) 2020/02/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid scores and-1, smiles for 76ers' crowd
